[0.000, "o", "\r\r\n      Generate an image from a text prompt using Ollama image model. Supports optional width, height, and steps parameters.\r\r\n  - whoami [safe]\r\r\n      Return agent identity and capabilities for self-awareness\r\r\n  - sage_task_status [safe]\r\r\n    "]
