[0.000, "o", "      Create a task for the sage agent to work on. Use this to break down complex requests into manageable steps.\r\r\n  - log_search_advanced [safe]\r\r\n      Search logs with multiple criteria: level, module, message pattern, tool name, and time range\r\r\n"]
