[0.000, "o", "# Petstore вЂ” demo project for guile-sage\r\r\n\r\r\nA tiny pet store API + CLI used to exercise guile-sage's tool suite in\r\r\ndemos and documentation. Not a real product.\r\r\n\r\r\n## Layout\r\r\n\r\r\n- `pet.py` вЂ” `Pet` data class\r\r\n- `store.py` вЂ” in-memory `Store` with add/get/list/remove\r\r\n- `api.py` вЂ” minimal HTTP handler (stdlib, no Flask dependency)\r\r\n- `cli.py` вЂ” command-line interface over the store\r\r\n- `test_pet.py` вЂ” unit tests (pytest-style, no fixtures)\r\r\n\r\r\n## Run\r\r\n\r\r\n```sh\r\r\npython3 cli.py add \"Fido\" dog\r\r\npython3 cli.py list\r\r\n```\r\r\n\r\r\n## Test\r\r\n\r\r\n```sh\r\r\npython3 -m pytest test_pet.py\r\r\n```\r\r\n\r\r\n\r\r\n"]
